361
00:20:54,720 --> 00:20:56,799
or if the scenery in the film

362
00:20:56,799 --> 00:20:57,640
speaks to you,

363
00:20:57,640 --> 00:21:01,799
I think the first thing is just to try.

364
00:21:01,799 --> 00:21:03,400
The path is made one step at a time.

365
00:21:03,400 --> 00:21:04,480
What matters is taking action,

366
00:21:04,480 --> 00:21:07,240
not obsessing over what to choose.

367
00:21:08,119 --> 00:21:09,960
Whether you choose the Tor des Géants

368
00:21:09,960 --> 00:21:12,279
or just go for a hike in a park,

369
00:21:12,279 --> 00:21:15,039
or even leave home and walk down an unfamiliar street,

370
00:21:15,039 --> 00:21:16,519
all of those things are good for you,

371
00:21:16,519 --> 00:21:17,920
as long as you go out and experience them,

372
00:21:17,920 --> 00:21:19,119
keep experiencing different things,

373
00:21:19,319 --> 00:21:20,359
and let them accumulate over time.

374
00:21:20,359 --> 00:21:23,000
I think you'll find your own path.

375
00:21:23,000 --> 00:21:24,920
It's not about finishing the Tor des Géants,

376
00:21:24,920 --> 00:21:26,720
or completing the PTL,

377
00:21:26,720 --> 00:21:28,799
as some ultimate goal.

378
00:21:28,960 --> 00:21:31,240
Don't make other people's goals your own.

379
00:21:31,240 --> 00:21:32,720
Even if you achieve them,

380
00:21:32,720 --> 00:21:35,119
you may not feel that happy.

381
00:21:35,119 --> 00:21:35,720
You may even find

382
00:21:35,720 --> 00:21:38,200
you don't know what to do next.

383
00:21:38,200 --> 00:21:40,480
In the course of your own exploration,

384
00:21:40,480 --> 00:21:41,640
you should have a style of your own.

385
00:21:43,000 --> 00:21:44,920
Don't think that nature

386
00:21:44,920 --> 00:21:47,599
has to mean mountains, seas, lakes, and so on.

387
00:21:47,599 --> 00:21:50,720
In fact, nature can be the city you live in,

388
00:21:50,720 --> 00:21:52,559
or the streets you walk every day.

389
00:21:52,559 --> 00:21:53,480
All of that is nature too.

390
00:21:55,000 --> 00:21:58,519
Don't just

391
00:21:58,519 --> 00:22:01,559
only through social media,

392
00:22:01,559 --> 00:22:02,720
and nature through social media.

393
00:22:02,720 --> 00:22:04,920
I think the best way is to go out and experience it,

394
00:22:04,920 --> 00:22:06,000
and experience more of it.

395
00:22:14,039 --> 00:22:14,839
Yes.

396
00:22:15,680 --> 00:22:16,480
Oh.

397
00:22:17,119 --> 00:22:17,920
Oh.

398
00:22:46,440 --> 00:22:47,839
Back when I first started running,

399
00:22:47,839 --> 00:22:48,799
whether it was a 100-kilometer race

400
00:22:48,799 --> 00:22:50,880
or navigating my own way through Wugong Mountain,

401
00:22:50,880 --> 00:22:52,720
when I was in the forest and hit spider webs,

402
00:22:53,079 --> 00:22:53,960
my energy dropped,

403
00:22:53,960 --> 00:22:55,680
and my face was covered with bugs,

404
00:22:55,680 --> 00:22:57,119
Getting tangled in spider webs was so frustrating.

405
00:22:57,880 --> 00:22:58,720
But that mindset

406
00:22:58,720 --> 00:23:01,119
gradually carried over into

407
00:23:01,119 --> 00:23:02,680
my Tor des Géants today.

408
00:23:02,680 --> 00:23:05,680
When I face darkness, fatigue, or injury,

409
00:23:05,680 --> 00:23:08,440
I have to keep adjusting myself,

410
00:23:08,440 --> 00:23:11,079
find a way to lift my spirits and get to the next aid station.

411
00:23:11,119 --> 00:23:12,319
It should be the process.

412
00:23:13,079 --> 00:23:14,119
All I can say is

413
00:23:14,240 --> 00:23:16,079
the memories this place left me are so beautiful.

414
00:23:16,079 --> 00:23:18,400
This place is truly beautiful.

415
00:23:18,480 --> 00:23:20,839
I'll try to come back every year.

416
00:23:20,839 --> 00:23:23,920
I'll keep training

417
00:23:23,920 --> 00:23:26,119
so that next time the experience can be even better,

418
00:23:26,279 --> 00:23:28,559
not so that I can get a better result.

419
00:23:28,559 --> 00:23:30,000
At the same time,

420
00:23:30,000 --> 00:23:31,799
I may become calmer.

421
00:23:31,799 --> 00:23:33,440
I think that's the goal I'm pursuing.

422
00:23:38,240 --> 00:23:39,960
After work every day,

423
00:23:39,960 --> 00:23:41,640
I run up the hill behind my workplace

424
00:23:41,759 --> 00:23:43,160
and watch the sunset from afar.

425
00:23:43,160 --> 00:23:44,440
I can see Qingshuijian Mountain.

426
00:23:44,440 --> 00:23:45,960
I don't think,

427
00:23:45,960 --> 00:23:47,640
the Alps are all that important.

428
00:23:47,640 --> 00:23:49,119
That's how I feel.

429
00:23:51,359 --> 00:23:53,079
Life is a,

430
00:23:53,079 --> 00:23:53,640
circle.

431
00:23:53,640 --> 00:23:55,920
Some people may draw a big circle

432
00:23:56,079 --> 00:23:57,000
and take many paths.
